  "text": "54-1 cells transduced with DUX4 or GFP lentivirus were treated 16 hr post-infection with 10 µM proteasome inhibitor MG132 (Sigma). Samples were collected 8 hr after MG132 treatment, and UPF1 levels were estimated by immunoblotting. Histone H3, which has a long half-life [CITATION_1] , was used as a loading control, in addition to the nonspecific band.",
